{"word":"G499 - ἀντίτυπον - antítypon - an-teet'-oo-pon - Figure","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀντίτυπον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">antítypon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-teet'-oo-pon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Figure</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அடையாளமான, ஒப்பனையான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"rough, harsh, obstinate, hostile a thing resembling another, its counterpart"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a compound of <a href=\"#/G473 - ἀντί - antí - an-tee'/473\">G473</a> and <a href=\"#/G5179 - τύπος - týpos - too'-pos/5179\">G5179</a>; <i>corresponding</i> (&ldquo;antitype&rdquo;), that is, a <i>representative</i>, <i>counterpart:</i> - (like) figure (whereunto).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G499/499\">G499</a>, <a href=\"#/G5179/5179\">G5179</a>, <a href=\"#/G5296/5296\">G5296</a>"}]}